# ─── LearnAI Environment Variables ───────────────────────────────────────────
# This project has separate .env files for each service:
#
# Backend (Spring Boot):
#   → Copy backened/.env.example to backened/.env
#
# Frontend:
#   → Copy frontend/.env.example to frontend/.env
#
# Python services use the same backend .env values
# (EMBEDDING_SERVICE_URL and SCRAPER_SERVICE_URL)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────